org.fluidity.composition.container.spi

Interface DependencyResolver

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DependencyGraph

    public interface DependencyResolver
extends DependencyGraph
    Implemented by a component container to allow a DependencyInjector to interact with that container.

    Usage

    You don't interact with an internal interface.

        Object cached(Class<?> api,
              ComponentContext context)
